ZH: 我们需要明天开会，也就是说，明天早上我们必须准时到达。
EN: We need to have a meeting tomorrow, which means we must arrive on time tomorrow morning.

ZH: 他迟到了半个小时，也就是说，他错过了部分讲座内容。
EN: He was half an hour late, which means he missed some of the lecture.

ZH: 这个人很有经验，也就是说，他能帮助我们解决问题。
EN: This person is very experienced, which means he can help us solve problems.

ZH: 我们需要更多的材料，也就是说，我们必须尽快采购。
EN: We need more materials, which means we must procure them as soon as possible.

ZH: 明天下雨，也就是说，我们要记得带伞。
EN: It will rain tomorrow, which means we need to remember to bring an umbrella.

ZH: 我们的计划改变了，也就是说，我们需要调整原来的时间安排。
EN: Our plan has changed, which means we need to adjust the original schedule.

ZH: 我们的生活方式决定了我们的健康水平，也就是说，我们要保持健康的生活方式。
EN: Our lifestyle determines our level of health, which means we need to maintain a healthy lifestyle.

ZH: 这个决定对整个团队都有影响，也就是说，我们必须共同努力。
EN: This decision has an impact on the entire team, which means we must work together.

ZH: 这个产品非常受欢迎，也就是说，我们需要扩大生产。
EN: This product is very popular, which means we need to expand production.

ZH: 我很忙，也就是说，我不能帮你完成这个任务。
EN: I am busy, which means I cannot help you complete this task.

ZH: 我们花了很多时间准备这次演讲，也就是说，我们不想失去这个机会。
EN: We spent a lot of time preparing for this presentation, which means we don't want to miss this opportunity.

ZH: 这个地方非常远，也就是说，我们需要安排交通工具。
EN: This place is very far, which means we need to arrange transportation.

ZH: 他们提供了很多有用的建议，也就是说，我们可以从他们的经验中学习到很多。
EN: They provided many useful suggestions, which means we can learn a lot from their experience.

ZH: 老师说得很清楚，也就是说，我们应该理解这个概念。
EN: The teacher explained it very clearly, which means we should understand this concept.

ZH: 这条路上有很多交通堵塞，也就是说，我们要提前出发。
EN: There is a lot of traffic congestion on this road, which means we should leave early.

ZH: 这个问题非常复杂，也就是说，我们需要更多的时间来研究。
EN: This problem is very complex, which means we need more time to study it.

ZH: 她是一个才华横溢的画家，也就是说，她的画作很有价值。
EN: She is a talented painter, which means her paintings are valuable.

ZH: 这个项目需要团队合作，也就是说，我们需要彼此支持。
EN: This project requires teamwork, which means we need to support each other.

ZH: 这个消息让我们感到震惊，也就是说，我们需要做好应对的准备。
EN: This news shocked us, which means we need to be prepared to deal with it.

ZH: 时间过得很快，也就是说，我们应该珍惜每一天。
EN: Time flies, which means we should cherish every day.
